_sText:
The skybox I used was the one most suited for the map, however there was a huge dev texture for the bottom so please ignore it. Anyway id just like to say that this is my first release. I've been practicing with hammer for a while now and i think this map is good enough to be submitted. So, download and enjoy.


I'd like to give credit to FAJ, for I've taken a few ides from his master exploder map...
